{"tid":16664,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"每日收工逼巴士都係一場生死戰","createTime":"2016-12-01T14:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T04:44:08.000Z","uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2136ef021840a708dab3d6ef82bc43b55ba8ed87","tid":16664,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"話說今日我同平時一樣咁等巴士收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實已經好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人既心情都唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死逼爛逼先上到架濕狗巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成程一人一格格仔咁企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班人好似運豬貨車上面d豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉貼肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後終於逼到去中途站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 散減d人<br />\n我見有位咪坐埋去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忽然有個女人眼甘甘望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌原來佢話佢想坐我個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要細細聲話我男人老狗後生仔同人爭位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪痴撚咗線嫁？我都返咗成日工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 企咗成日架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估得你需要個位咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日都係咁真係命都短幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942759f03bb93012dce537b1b76444bc243c827","tid":16664,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"利伸：90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677c754f29916ba3b2e15